{"about_the_game":"<strong>Gateway is an award-winning minimalist point &amp; click puzzle adventure set in a desolate black void. The Gateway Trilogy includes remastered versions of the first two games \u2013 plus a never-before-seen third installment.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661470/extras/ezgif-2-685ae5ff09aa.gif?t=1711879072\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gateway</h2>Gateway has a deceptively simple premise: guide a character through a series of rooms, solve puzzles to progress. But underneath the stark presentation lurks hidden convolutions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661470/extras/ezgif-2-f921c7007c5d.gif?t=1711879072\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gateway I &amp; II</h2>Gateway I &amp; II were originally released as freeware back in 2006 and 2007. For the trilogy edition they have been completely remastered with enhancements to sound, gameplay and visuals \u2013 along with the addition of a never-before-seen third installment.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2>If you've never played the previous Gateway games, this is by far the best way to experience them. If you've already played them, don't miss the chance to experience them again in this spruced up and expanded edition.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/661470/extras/ezgif-2-e9dee2ce9bf9.gif?t=1711879072\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gateway III</h2>Gateway III \u2013 the lengthiest installment in the series by far \u2013 is a completely new addition that loosely builds upon the previous games in surprising and discomforting ways.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Trilogy: Enjoy an entirely new part of the quietly unsettling Gateway series<br></li><li>Remastered: Appreciate the reworked music, gameplay and visuals<br></li><li>Story: Experience strange and ambiguous stories<br></li><li>Puzzles: Solve tricky puzzles in an abstract minimalist void<br></li><li>Hard mode: Tackle 40 extra devious puzzles if you feel up for the challenge<br></li><li>Commentary: Listen to the creator outline the choices behind the game's design</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Remotely True","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/661470/4a286406365ac409e613eb948e1e2a9bcbc4deb7.jpg"},{"name":"Commentary","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/661470/7152d96fd024100e947b1d71c556299d21b9b01f.jpg"},{"name":"Not THAT Easy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/661470/d25bec2cd4230cdf903dbecfb5a34ee36cc87ddb.jpg"},{"name":"Clueless I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/661470/64c91070b2bf48de92b2b7cc097b8c424726953e.jpg"},{"name":"We Need To Go Deeper","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/661470/5c7a411a88a90e35c6e34134bd91bf8f5921c2c0.jpg"},{"name":"Video Tape I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/661470/0b8ce5076ec6ba35fe5b0c111bc705be4b54441f.jpg"},{"name":"Video Tape II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/661470/b96cb47a58032829daf865fd69c00a0d90125179.jpg"},{"name":"Video Tape III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/661470/71a9ac967beb2869415a80086a3c09f9946be070.jpg"},{"name":"Video Tape IV","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/661470/0b72243265acd16a8a71dcdd6e2bf9045d06679f.jpg"},{"name":"Shockingly Humane","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/661470/7ee21cc16d9d962035bf61783ff7f8af64a377f7.jpg"}],"total":33},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/661470?t=1711879072","back